    "For instance, an online clothes company can analyze consumer data to detect fashion preferences and send customized emails or ads promoting matching products.",
    "AI-powered recommendation systems also help personalize marketing.",
    "These engines use consumer data and browsing activity to recommend products, upsell/cross-sell, and relevant content.",
    "Showing items and services that match client interests promotes conversions and customer satisfaction.",
    "Natural language processing and sentiment analysis allow AI to assess customer involvement and sentiment."
